            "title": "台股創新高首越36000點收市 單日漲838點或2.37%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股雙喜臨門，台灣加權指數創新高並首次升越36000點收市，亦成功完成六連升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230704_FI_source-licensed_TaiwanStock.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230704_FI_source-licensed_TaiwanStock.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">指數裂口高開過百點後升幅迅速擴大，未幾已突破36000點，其後不斷試頂，最高見36341點，升884點；收報36296點，升幅仍達838點或2.37%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15870898-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98%e9%a6%96%e8%b6%8a36000%e9%bb%9e%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82-%e5%96%ae%e6%97%a5%e6%bc%b2838%e9%bb%9e%e6%88%962-37",
